ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Change of boundary of the Medicine Hat & District Chamber of Commerce, in Alberta
PrecisOrder approving the application by the Medicine Hat & District Chamber of Commerce, in Alberta, to change the boundaries of its district from City of Medicine Hat, the Town of Redcliff and the Municipal District of Cypress County, which includes Wild Horse, Seven Persons, Elkwater, Irvine, Walsh, Dunmore, Schuler, Hilda, Suffield, Ralston, Veinerville and Desert Blume to City of Medicine Hat, the Town of Redcliff and the Municipal District of Cypress County, which includes Wild Horse, Seven Persons, Elkwater, Irvine, Walsh, Dunmore, Schuler, Hilda, Suffield, Ralston, Veinerville Desert Blume, the municipalities of Brooks, County of Newell, Town of Bassano, Village of Duchess, and Village of Rosemary.
AttachmentsAttachment
